- Okay. Okay!

1390
01:52:20,866 --> 01:52:25,370
[Growling]

1391
01:52:25,454 --> 01:52:29,416
- [Growling]
- [Men Shouting]

1392
01:52:34,671 --> 01:52:35,714
Tie him down

1393
01:52:38,425 --> 01:52:41,512
Help, Elliott, help!

1394
01:52:43,430 --> 01:52:46,683
Man this harpoon. Take this.
[Chuckling]

1395
01:52:48,644 --> 01:52:51,563
Light the fuse.

1396
