<i>Get out of the way!</i>

1402
01:53:26,723 --> 01:53:28,934
- [Whimpering]
- [Screaming]

1403
01:53:33,480 --> 01:53:35,858
He's going!
Let me get a bead on him!

1404
01:53:38,944 --> 01:53:43,198
